<br />
<h4 class="text-center">Thank you for enjoying our products.</h4>
<img src="~/Images/FlowerLogo.png" width="50" style="margin-left:600px"/> 
<h4>Your order is due to be delivered to you between @Model.DeliveryEarliestDate and @Model.DeliveryLatestDate</h4>